data.name: tbGAC.Text
data.value: If you plan to use CUDAfy from a service you will need to install CUDAfy.NET.dll in the Global Assembly Cache. If you do not you will get a "Failed to resolve assembly" exception when translating code with CudafyTranslator.Cudafy(...) Please also be aware of restrictions on GPU use in certain scenarios (e.g. from within SQL or from Remote Desktop).
